        whole website (front-end and back-end) from scratch to the deployment
        and maintenance.
      </p>
      <h3>Part-time full-stack developer trainee</h3>
      <p>
        Developer of the “Ontag” project, an open-source tool for journalists
        aimed to give answers to relevant questions through annotations on news
        articles. Part of a multidisciplinary and international team formed by
        journalists and sociologists of Common Action Forum and computer
        engineers of the Ontology Engineering Group.
      </p>
